---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import SectionHero from '../components/SectionHero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Factory Transformation | Navvi Corporations" description="Save ₹3-10 Cr annually with Navvi factory transformation: assessment, 90-day sprint, KPI dashboards and on-floor execution for garment manufacturers.">
  <main>
    <SectionHero eyebrow="Factory transformation" title="Save ₹3-10 Cr annually by fixing quality, efficiency, delay and cash leaks." lead="Navvi combines consulting, implementation staff, KPI dashboards, training and daily control. We work on the factory floor, not only in presentations." primaryLabel="Book free assessment" primaryHref="https://wa.me/919894466715?text=Hello%20Navvi%2C%20I%20want%20a%20free%20factory%20assessment." image="/assets/hero/hero-factory.jpg" imageAlt="Factory transformation team on the production floor">
      <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/case-results/">View results</a>
    </SectionHero>
    <section class="section"><div class="container grid-3" data-reveal-group><article class="card card-featured" data-reveal><span class="kicker">Free audit</span><h3>Factory assessment</h3><p class="muted">Walk-through, KPI gap map, improvement opportunity list and 90-day action sketch.</p></article><article class="card"><span class="kicker">Pilot</span><h3>1-week implementation sprint</h3><p class="muted">On-floor quick wins with supervisors and short-term support where your team needs help.</p></article><article class="card"><span class="kicker">90 days</span><h3>Transformation sprint</h3><p class="muted">Line balance, zero-defect gates, flow redesign, scheduler, dashboards and owner review rhythm.</p></article></div></section>
    <section class="section section-blue visual-band"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">KPI focus</p><h2>Numbers we improve.</h2></div><div class="grid-3"><div class="card card-blue"><h3>Quality</h3><p>Right First Time, DHU, returns and defect recurrence.</p></div><div class="card card-blue"><h3>Efficiency</h3><p>OWE, SAM control, line balance, output per head and cost per minute.</p></div><div class="card card-blue"><h3>Delivery</h3><p>OTIF, order lead time, plan adherence and dispatch readiness.</p></div><div class="card card-blue"><h3>Cash</h3><p>CCC, inventory days, fabric utilization and process loss.</p></div><div class="card card-blue"><h3>People</h3><p>Absenteeism, attrition, engagement, skill matrix and training readiness.</p></div><div class="card card-blue"><h3>Systems</h3><p>Power BI dashboards, no-code data capture, SOPs and review routines.</p></div></div></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container split"><div><p class="eyebrow">Support system</p><h2>Not just advice. We fill execution gaps.</h2><p class="muted">If the factory does not have the right staff ready, Navvi can support implementation with fabric follow-up, junior merchandising, quality control, supervision and dashboard setup.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>What comes with the sprint</h3><ul class="list"><li>Loss tree and ranked action plan.</li><li>Dashboard starter from ERP, Excel or no-code capture.</li><li>Line balance and daily review rhythm.</li><li>SOP mini-pack and supervisor training.</li><li>Risk reversal terms agreed before engagement.</li></ul></div></div></section>
  </main>
</Layout>
